"{\"uid\": \"citizen.co.za-sport-wayde-van-niekerk-200m-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Home\\u00bbSport ByWesley Botton Chief sports journalist 3 minute read 11 July 2024 01:25 pm Former Olympic 400m champion Wayde van Niekerk at the Diamond League meeting in London last season.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"score\": 0.901131173431149, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Botton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botton,_North_Yorkshire\"}, {\"begin\": 122, \"end\": 139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wayde van Niekerk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999932111605516, \"rank\": 6.7773944136473725e-06, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 173, \"end\": 179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9968045915559118, \"rank\": 0.0032049382689215097, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"3 minute\", \"from\": 51, \"to\": 59}, {\"ngram\": \"London\", \"from\": 167, \"to\": 173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Picture: Pat Scaasi/MI News/NurPhoto/AFP At first, when Wayde van Niekerk's name was removed from the list of qualifiers in the 400m for the Olympic Games, I assumed it was a mistake.\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 206, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Scaasi\", \"score\": 0.9999999991964614, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scaasi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Scaasi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arnold_Scaasi\"}, {\"begin\": 250, \"end\": 267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wayde van Niekerk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wayde_van_Niekerk\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Picture\", \"from\": 193, \"to\": 200}, {\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifiers\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 313}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 347}, {\"ngram\": \"a mistake\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taking various things into consideration, however, it actually makes some sense for theversatile sprinterto run the 200m event.\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"various things\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 400}, {\"ngram\": \"consideration\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 419}, {\"ngram\": \"some sense\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"theversatile sprinterto\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m event\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eight years after breaking the world record at the Rio Olympics, Van Niekerk remains more than capable over the 400m distance, having reached the final at the last two editions of the World Athletics Championships.\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999997278337, \"rank\": 2.7206430262800385e-10, \"text\": \"Rio Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999999976353138, \"rank\": 2.2222121059178017e-09, \"text\": \"World Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Niekerk\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 584}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m distance\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"the last two editions\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has struggled to regain his best form in recent years, however, after recovering from a long-term knee injury, and he has battled to shake off persistent niggles.\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his best form\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"a long-term knee injury\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"persistent niggles\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 888}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This has placed some doubt over his ability to step on the podium at major global championships, due to the strain on his body caused by racing over three rounds in the brutal 400m sprint.\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some doubt\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"his ability\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"major global championships\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"the strain\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"his body\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"over three rounds\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"the brutal 400m sprint\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And after he wasremoved this weekfrom the list of 400m qualifiers provided byWorld Athletics, it seems he's opting for the 200m instead (an event which he has admittedly always preferred racing).\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"400m qualifiers\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"byWorld Athletics\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"an event\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By competing over 200m in Paris, it will not only be less taxing on the former world champion, but it expands the nation's depth in the 4x100m and 4x400m relays, giving him the option of running either relay or both of them.\", \"from\": 1278, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999632509577, \"rank\": 3.674913353080639e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"over 200m\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"the former world champion\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation's depth\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"relays\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"the option\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"either relay\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa will not be expecting a lot of medals on the track in Paris, and putting together the best possible relay quartets could be key to ensuring the national athletics team break their seven-year podium drought at major championships.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999883159689956, \"rank\": 5.59114227641396e-06, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999632509577, \"rank\": 3.674913353080639e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1544}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"the best possible relay quartets\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"the national athletics team\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"their seven-year podium drought\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"major championships\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the age of 31, Van Niekerk is also past his prime, and his chances of securing a medal in individual events are slim, but he still has a lot to offer either of the sprint relay squads (or both), which might be his best chance of returning to the Olympic podium.\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 2012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Niekerk\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"his prime\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"his chances\", \"from\": 1806, \"to\": 1817}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"individual events\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1858}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"either\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"the sprint relay squads\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1934}, {\"ngram\": \"his best chance\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1976}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic podium\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So his absence in the individual 400m event is not only a wise decision for Van Niekerk, but it's also the best choice for the SA team.\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2141, \"end\": 2143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999161766517, \"rank\": 7.713891322853129e-08, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his absence\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual 400m event\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2057}, {\"ngram\": \"a wise decision\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Niekerk\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"the best choice\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A win-win situation.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A win-win situation\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Add The Citizen as a Preferred Source on Google and follow us on Google News to see more of our trusted reporting in Google News and Top Stories.\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2213, \"end\": 2219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9617816544706655, \"rank\": 0.03972729622444583, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 2237, \"end\": 2248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google News\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google